(121, 'Associacion Sevillana de Amigos del Ferrocarril', ' AlamilloÂ´s Railway is an small railway which is being installed in the city of Seville (Andalusia, Spain) It is a railway located in AlamilloÂ´s Park, in Cartuja Island, which is maintained by Andalusian Government. The works of building are next to be finished and we think that the inauguration will be that summer. The line will be 450 meters long with a track of 5"( inches), the same of 127mm.', 3, '', 'Parque de Alamillo', '41092', 'Sevilla', 14, 37.4215, -5.99759, 1, '', '63', 'ferrocarrildelalamillo.com', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
